Class DidasJpaRealmProvider

java.lang.Object
org.keycloak.models.jpa.JpaRealmProvider
com.ubicua.didas.resources.DidasJpaRealmProvider
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.keycloak.models.ClientProvider, org.keycloak.models.ClientScopeProvider, org.keycloak.models.DeploymentStateProvider, org.keycloak.models.GroupProvider, org.keycloak.models.RealmProvider, org.keycloak.models.RoleProvider, org.keycloak.provider.Provider, org.keycloak.storage.client.ClientLookupProvider, org.keycloak.storage.clientscope.ClientScopeLookupProvider, org.keycloak.storage.group.GroupLookupProvider, org.keycloak.storage.role.RoleLookupProvider
public class DidasJpaRealmProvider extends org.keycloak.models.jpa.JpaRealmProvider
JPA-based RealmProvider customized to insert DID discovery metadata when creating client roles.

Overrides addClientRole(ClientModel, String, String) to:

  1. Create a RoleEntity with given ID and name.
  2. Wrap it in DidasRoleAdapter for attribute handling.
  3. Invoke addAttributes(com.ubicua.didas.resources.DidasRoleAdapter, org.keycloak.models.ClientModel, java.lang.String) to add default DID attributes based on component configuration.

Author:
Ivan Kuchumov
